video.title: The 100
video.synopsis: A century after Earth was devastated by a nuclear apocalypse, 100 space station residents are sent to the planet to determine whether it's habitable.

episodes.synopsis: One hundred young exiles from a dying space station are sent to Earth 97 years after a nuclear apocalypse to test if the planet is now inhabitable.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Having discovered that Jasper may still be alive, Clarke, Bellamy, Octavia, Finn and Monty set out on a mission to locate their friend.
episodes.title: Earth Skills

episodes.synopsis: A fast-moving, toxic fog jeopardizes a mission to find a substance that could save Jasper's life. Clarke learns the truth about her father's betrayal.
episodes.title: Earth Kills

episodes.synopsis: After a shocking death, Clarke and Finn grow closer. Bellamy must keep the group from turning on one another and Abby takes a huge risk.
episodes.title: Murphy's Law

episodes.synopsis: After exposing Kane’s plan to reduce the population of the Ark, Abby and Jaha realize at least some of the 100 must still be alive.
episodes.title: Twilight's Last Gleaming

episodes.synopsis: Bellamy and his crew run into Grounder territory as they search for Octavia while Raven notices the deep connection between Finn and Clarke.
episodes.title: His Sister's Keeper

episodes.synopsis: Abby guides Clarke through a dangerous procedure while Diana Sydney takes her place as Chancellor. Kane agonizes over his recent decision.
episodes.title: Contents Under Pressure

episodes.synopsis: Some of the 100 lose touch with reality after eating a hallucinogen. One of them is tasked to kill, and Diana Sydney's treachery is revealed.
episodes.title: Day Trip

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Finn attempt to broker peace with the Grounders while others prepare for battle. Meanwhile, tragedy strikes the Unity Day celebration.
episodes.title: Unity Day

episodes.synopsis: John Murphy returns claiming to have been held captive by the Grounders and Clarke and Bellamy have different ideas on how to handle his return.
episodes.title: I Am Become Death

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Finn lead a hunt for food, Raven makes Bellamy an offer he can’t refuse, and Kane risks his life and reunites with Jaha and Abby.
episodes.title: The Calm

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Finn are confronted by a new enemy, Bellamy makes a heroic move to save Jasper, while those on the Ark face the inevitable.
episodes.title: We Are Grounders: Part I

episodes.synopsis: As the conflict escalates, Clarke pleads with Bellamy to do the right thing. Octavia makes a difficult choice. Raven and Jasper work against time.
episodes.title: We Are Grounders: Part II

episodes.synopsis: Trapped in the white room, Clarke tries to make sense of her surroundings. The Ark survivors face moral and physical dilemmas. An old enemy returns.
episodes.title: The 48

episodes.synopsis: A suspicious Clarke confronts President Dante Wallace and demands answers. Kane interrogates one of the 100, and Abby performs emergency surgery.
episodes.title: Inclement Weather

episodes.synopsis: Clarke teams with an unlikely ally after making a horrific discovery about Mount Weather's medical ward. Abby confesses to a crime.
episodes.title: Reapercussions

episodes.synopsis: After a betrayal, Clarke takes matters into her own hands, Bellamy, Finn and Murphy race to save a stranger and tensions rise between Raven and Wick.
episodes.title: Many Happy Returns

episodes.synopsis: Kane leads a mission to make peace with the Grounders, Jasper participates in a risky experiment and President Dante Wallace issues a warning.
episodes.title: Human Trials

episodes.synopsis: Raven learns that Mount Weather is causing communication interference, tempers flare between Clarke and Finn, and traitors surround President Wallace.
episodes.title: Fog of War

episodes.synopsis: Abby prepares a leap of faith to save her people from a Grounder assault. Meanwhile, Bellamy and Octavia share a shocking secret with Clarke.
episodes.title: Long into an Abyss

episodes.synopsis: A riot breaks out over Finn's actions as Abby and others decide whether to put him on trial or turn him over to the Grounders for torture.
episodes.title: Spacewalker

episodes.synopsis: Clarke strikes a deal with Lexa and Indra while the newly formed alliance between the Sky People and the Grounders is threatened.
episodes.title: Remember Me

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Lexa encounter a new enemy, Bellamy and Lincoln work together to break into Mount Weather and Indra makes Octavia an appealing offer.
episodes.title: Survival of the Fittest

episodes.synopsis: Bellamy and Lincoln's actions have brutal consequences, Abby fights to stay in control and a desperate Jasper confronts President Wallace.
episodes.title: Coup de Grace

episodes.synopsis: Tensions between Clarke and Abby come to a head, Raven helps Bellamy navigate Mount Weather and Jaha and Murphy encounter a stranger.
episodes.title: Rubicon

episodes.synopsis: Clarke questions Lexa's leadership decisions, Abby struggles to help an injured Kane while Jasper steps into a leadership role.
episodes.title: Resurrection

episodes.synopsis: Desperate for help, Raven summons Wick. Jaha and Murphy encounter a perilous roadblock, and Bellamy is in a race against time at Mount Weather.
episodes.title: Bodyguard of Lies

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Lexa prepare for battle, while Raven and Wick experience a major setback. Meanwhile, Octavia and Lincoln must make a difficult decision.
episodes.title: Blood Must Have Blood: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The journey to the City of Light continues as Jaha makes a move that shocks Murphy, Clarke receives unexpected help and Lincoln gets his revenge.
episodes.title: Blood Must Have Blood: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Bellamy and Kane head out on a mission to save Clarke, who has a bounty on her head. Murphy encounters Jaha at the mansion.
episodes.title: Wanheda: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Bellamy and Kane risk their lives to rescue Clarke. Abby considers opening Mount Weather as a medical facility. Murphy plans a betrayal.
episodes.title: Wanheda: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Clarke wrestles with a difficult decision. Meanwhile, Bellamy learns that something isn't what it seems.
episodes.title: Ye Who Enter Here

episodes.synopsis: Clarke uncovers the architect of a clever plot. While Kane tries to maintain peace, Jasper spirals out of control.
episodes.title: Watch the Thrones

episodes.synopsis: As Pike tightens his grip, Clarke races to stop a brewing war and a familiar face returns to Arkadia with a new mission. Murphy plays a risky game.
episodes.title: Hakeldama

episodes.synopsis: Clarke must decide between exacting revenge and making peace. Octavia and Kane team up, and Abby is concerned about Raven.
episodes.title: Bitter Harvest

episodes.synopsis: Clarke makes a discovery that changes everything. Lexa attempts to maintain stability among the clans. A dark chapter from the past is revealed.
episodes.title: Thirteen

episodes.synopsis: As Kane tries to find a peaceful solution, he comes to realize that he might have to take a more drastic course. Raven wants Jasper's help.
episodes.title: Terms and Conditions

episodes.synopsis: While Clarke makes an alarming discovery, Octavia faces a decision that could have dire consequences. Abby and Kane share a moment.
episodes.title: Stealing Fire

episodes.synopsis: Jaha takes a frightening new approach in his efforts to recruit Abby. Bellamy faces a difficult truth, and Monty lands in a dangerous situation.
episodes.title: Fallen

episodes.synopsis: While Jasper's rage grows, Raven's dark side emerges under the influence of ALIE. Octavia tries to figure out her place in the world.
episodes.title: Nevermore

episodes.synopsis: Jaha returns to Polis, and Murphy has a surprise encounter. Meanwhile, Octavia uncovers a clue.
episodes.title: Demons

episodes.synopsis: Clarke embarks on a mission that could change everything. Murphy gains insight that may be the key to his survival, and Kane reaches his limit.
episodes.title: Join or Die

episodes.synopsis: Clarke, Bellamy, Octavia and Jasper face a devastating obstacle, while Raven and Monty make a key discovery.
episodes.title: Red Sky at Morning

episodes.synopsis: In Part 1 of the two-part season finale, Clarke finds hope in the most unlikely place. Meanwhile, ALIE's master plan comes together.
episodes.title: Perverse Instantiation: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: In the second half of the two-part season finale, the group prepares for a final showdown as they begin to face the reality of their tragic situation.
episodes.title: Finale: Perverse Instantiation: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Trapped in Polis and surrounded by hostile Azgeda, Clarke devises a risky plan. Meanwhile, Raven discovers the grave new threat facing them all.
episodes.title: Echoes

episodes.synopsis: Roan takes a risky stand to buy time for Skaikru's secret work, and Bellamy and Clarke face tough choices that imperil the survival of them all.
episodes.title: Heavy Lies the Crown

episodes.synopsis: With the radiation closing in, Jaha leads Clarke and Bellamy on a long-odds mission to find a refuge. Roan sends Octavia to retrieve the stolen Flame.
episodes.title: The Four Horsemen

episodes.synopsis: Clarke's lies foment a revolt, Abby leads a risky quest to find Nightblood, and Octavia faces a showdown when the clans' alliance disintegrates.
episodes.title: A Lie Guarded

episodes.synopsis: With the alliance broken, Roan and his Azgeda army march on Skaikru's base, forcing Clarke into a desperate gamble to avoid an all-out war.
episodes.title: The Tinder Box

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Roan lead a dangerous sortie to deliver precious fuel for Raven's Nightblood mission, and Octavia faces her consuming thirst for revenge.
episodes.title: We Will Rise

episodes.synopsis: As lethal black rain falls, Abby seeks a last-ditch radiation cure, Octavia connects with Ilian, and Bellamy faces a life-or-death decision.
episodes.title: Gimme Shelter

episodes.synopsis: As time grows short, Clarke takes drastic action to find a cure. Looking for a secret bunker, Kane and Jaha face a doomsday cult's cryptic riddle.
episodes.title: God Complex

episodes.synopsis: Betrayal and bad blood drive the clans toward a deadly showdown, Octavia struggles to renounce her violent past, and Raven chooses her fate.
episodes.title: DNR

episodes.synopsis: Octavia, Roan and warriors from every clan fight to the death in a ritual battle for control of the bunker -- but not everyone plays by the rules.
episodes.title: Die All, Die Merrily

episodes.synopsis: Octavia stalls the clans for time while Bellamy defies Clarke's plan for the bunker. Monty tries to save Jasper. Raven discovers unexpected hope.
episodes.title: The Other Side

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Bellamy lead a perilous mission to rescue Raven. Kane and Jaha clash over selecting survivors. Abby makes a fateful decision.
episodes.title: The Chosen

episodes.synopsis: As Praimfaya strikes, Octavia assumes command of the bunker, and Raven leads Clarke's stranded team on a last-minute race to escape destruction.
episodes.title: Praimfaya

episodes.synopsis: Struggling to survive alone in a world scorched by Praimfaya, Clarke makes a startling discovery -- and faces a dangerous new threat.
episodes.title: Eden

episodes.synopsis: Octavia spills blood to establish her command when overcrowded conditions and violent clan tensions turn the bunker into an underground war zone.
episodes.title: Red Queen

episodes.synopsis: Diyoza's invaders go on the hunt to take over the valley from Clarke. Raven's crew makes an alarming discovery aboard the orbiting mystery ship.
episodes.title: Sleeping Giants

episodes.synopsis: A tenuous pact teeters on collapse during a mission to liberate the bunker. Raven and Murphy face a dire choice aboard the Eligius IV.
episodes.title: Pandora's Box

episodes.synopsis: While a rift among her soldiers widens, Diyoza puts Abby to the test. Octavia clashes with Clarke, who discovers a gruesome new threat.
episodes.title: Shifting Sands

episodes.synopsis: A surprise overture from Diyoza puts Octavia's ironfisted leadership to the test. Clarke turns to an unexpected ally for help protecting Madi.
episodes.title: Exit Wounds

episodes.synopsis: Clarke turns to Indra after discovering Octavia's barbaric plan to conquer the valley. Echo forces Raven's hand to initiate Monty's cyberattack.
episodes.title: Acceptable Losses

episodes.synopsis: While Octavia finalizes her battle plans, Clarke makes a treacherous play to prevent war. Abby pleads for Raven's help after making a breakthrough.
episodes.title: How We Get to Peace

episodes.synopsis: Murphy lights a fire that sparks calamitous events in Shallow Valley. The widening schisms forming in Wonkru worsen and may become permanent.
episodes.title: Sic Semper Tyrannis

episodes.synopsis: Clarke races to keep Madi safe while Octavia forces Bellamy, Indra and Gaia into a violent showdown. Abby fights a desperate personal battle.
episodes.title: The Warriors Will

episodes.synopsis: Clarke scrambles to save Abby, who reveals a ghastly secret from the bunker. The converging armies prepare for a climactic battle for Shallow Valley.
episodes.title: The Dark Year

episodes.synopsis: As battle erupts, a betrayal leads to catastrophe. Madi defies Clarke over the fate of Wonkru. Octavia faces the consequences of her recklessness.
episodes.title: Damocles: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: After the disaster in the gorge, Wonkru unites under Madi for a final assault while McCreary's lunatic plan leads to a fate-changing revelation.
episodes.title: Damocles: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After a century of cryosleep, the survivors begin exploring the wonders -- and cryptic dangers -- of their mysterious new home, Planet Alpha.
episodes.title: Sanctum

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Bellamy's plan to survive the eclipse quickly falls to pieces. Raven turns to Diyoza to thwart an attack aboard the Eligius IV.
episodes.title: Red Sun Rising

episodes.synopsis: Clarke tries diplomacy with the circumspect leader of Sanctum. Outside the barrier, a band of mysterious raiders threatens the jump ship.
episodes.title: The Children of Gabriel

episodes.synopsis: Sanctum's cryptic renewal celebration portends a fresh start for Clarke and the others, but a jarring surprise awaits. Octavia plans a daring escape.
episodes.title: The Face Behind the Glass

episodes.synopsis: Jordan follows his suspicions while Josephine schemes to advance the Primes' troubling agenda. On the run, Diyoza and Octavia stumble into a new peril.
episodes.title: The Gospel of Josephine

episodes.synopsis: Murphy and Abby entertain tempting offers from Josephine. Diyoza and Octavia discover a cryptic clue to the anomaly. Madi's visions take a dark turn.
episodes.title: Memento Mori

episodes.synopsis: Clarke faces a reckoning with her memories -- and a battle for supremacy over Josephine -- in the dreamlike arena of her mindspace.
episodes.title: Nevermind

episodes.synopsis: Diyoza and Octavia follow Xavier into Gabriel's dark secret. Raven confronts Abby over her plan to save Kane. Murphy's deal forces a showdown.
episodes.title: The Old Man and the Anomaly

episodes.synopsis: Bellamy tries leveraging his way into a parley with Gabriel, Kane makes a grim decision, and Octavia comes face-to-face with her troubled conscience.
episodes.title: What You Take with You

episodes.synopsis: Revolution brews against the Primes as they plan retaliation for Kane. Clarke and Josephine fight for survival as the body they share nears death.
episodes.title: Matryoshka

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and Gabriel form a risky plan to sow panic inside Sanctum. Echo tells Ryker the truth about her past. Octavia tries to make amends with Bellamy.
episodes.title: Ashes to Ashes

episodes.synopsis: As an attack force gathers outside Sanctum to prevent more Naming Day killings, Clarke poses as Josephine in a risky attempt to lower the shield.
episodes.title: Adjustment Protocol

episodes.synopsis: Gabriel and the others combat the true believers remaining in Sanctum. Clarke scrambles to prevent the Primes from escaping aboard the Eligius IV.
episodes.title: The Blood of Sanctum

episodes.synopsis: Volatile schisms subvert Clarke's first efforts to rebuild Sanctum. Hope helps Echo and Gabriel track an invisible foe in a frantic hunt for Bellamy.
episodes.title: From the Ashes

episodes.synopsis: Time moves in mysterious ways through the anomaly, where Octavia makes a breakthrough discovery and — much later — so does Gabriel.
episodes.title: The Garden

episodes.synopsis: Russell's followers foment violence as he prepares to meet his fate. Meanwhile, a faulty nuclear reactor endangers all of Sanctum.
episodes.title: False Gods

episodes.synopsis: Using time dilation on the anomaly's far side, Hope, Echo and Gabriel prepare for an attack on Bardo. Clarke hazards a deal with the Disciples.
episodes.title: Hesperides

episodes.synopsis: Octavia gets a punishing welcome to the marvels of Bardo, while Indra tangles with fanatics in Sanctum and makes an unnerving discovery.
episodes.title: Welcome to Bardo

episodes.synopsis: Diyoza fights to escape imprisonment on Bardo, Indra confronts growing hostilities in Sanctum, and Clarke's team stumbles into trouble on a new world.
episodes.title: Nakara

episodes.synopsis: Murphy plays a tense game with Russell while Emori lays plans to heal the fractures in Sanctum. Diyoza and Hope have a reckoning on Bardo.
episodes.title: The Queen's Gambit

episodes.synopsis: Not long after Earth's nuclear apocalypse, Becca unravels the Anomaly Stone's code, and the original Grounders spark a rebellion against Second Dawn.
episodes.title: Anaconda

episodes.synopsis: Consenting to train as Disciples for a coming war, Diyoza and the others learn the secrets of Bardo. A hostage crisis forces a showdown in Sanctum.
episodes.title: The Flock

episodes.synopsis: In the wake of a bloody massacre in Sanctum, Sheidheda tries to snatch control from Indra. Meanwhile, Echo devises a devious plan on Bardo.
episodes.title: A Little Sacrifice

episodes.synopsis: Seeking passage off a mysterious world, two travelers fight their way up a treacherous mountainside — and make a momentous discovery along the way.
episodes.title: Etherea

episodes.synopsis: While Sheidheda launches a violent purge in Sanctum, the Shepherd's newest convert strikes a deal: locate the Flame to save the lives of his friends.
episodes.title: The Stranger

episodes.synopsis: The Shepherd assails Sanctum to force Clarke to retrieve the Flame. An eclipse revitalizes an old menace. Gabriel has a breakthrough epiphany.
episodes.title: Blood Giant

episodes.synopsis: Clarke and the others find a surprising world on the far side of the portal. Sheidheda agrees to help the Shepherd target Madi. Octavia faces her past.
episodes.title: A Sort of Homecoming

episodes.synopsis: While Emori fights for her life and Clarke tries to return to Bardo, the Shepherd probes Madi's mind for the final code that will trigger the Last War.
episodes.title: The Dying of the Light

episodes.synopsis: Jordan helps Raven and Indra plan a final showdown with Bardo's army, while Clarke faces a harrowing trial that will decide the fate of them all.
episodes.title: The Last War
